        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "Launched by the All India Council for Technical Education, AICTE e-Shodh Sindhu Scheme (eSS) provides  subscriptions of e-Resources like Web of Science, Scopus, The American Society of Mechanical Engineers (ASME), American Society of Civil Engineers (ASCE) and Bentham Science to institutions.\n**Objective:**\nFacilitating access to e-Resource to the students, faculty and researchers, a new to augment the culture of research in the institution and overall quality of technical education.\n",
        "benefits_md": "**Benefits:** Subscriptions of e-Resources like Web of Science, Scopus, ASME, ASCE and Bentham Science to institutions.\n<br>\n\n**Duration of Subscriptions:** Initially for one calendar year, renewable for further year on the basis of usage by institute and fulfilments of other essential eligibility criteria.\n",
